##Clustering using loop

set.seed(123)
silhouette_coefficients <- numeric(0)
for (k in 2:5) {
  kmc <- kmeans(fds, k)
  ci <- intCriteria(fds, kmc$cluster, "Silhouette")
  print(paste("Silhouette coefficient for", k, "clusters:", ci))
  silhouette_coefficients <- c(silhouette_coefficients, ci)
}
